INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (159, '信息工程学院开展“过政治生日、忆入党初心”活动', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">11</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">18</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">日下午，信息工程学院党总支在学院党员之家开展</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">“过政治生日、忆入党初心”活动。学院党总支副书记、院长朱立才，党总支副书记、</span></span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">副</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">院长</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">姜琳，副院长周彩根</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">以及</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">1</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">名</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">11</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月份入党的教师党员</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">贾铮</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">参加会议，第一党支部全体党员列席会议。会议由党总支书记赵任凭主持。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">活动在庄严的国际歌声中开始。朱立才向贾铮同志赠送政治生日贺卡，对他参加工作以来为学院发展作出的贡献表示感谢，肯定他作为年轻教师积极上进、不断进取的工作态度，勉励他不忘入党初心，永葆党员本色，再接再厉，在学院搭建的平台中继续发挥正能量，把自身发展与学院发展相结合，为学院</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">“十四五”规划工作的开展贡献力量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">贾铮同志深情回顾了自己的入党动机、初心和工作历程。他表示将始终铭记党员身份，牢记党员使命，践行党员义务，坚定理想信念，用实际行动践行入党誓言，努力在学院、学校各项工作中，积极发挥党员的先锋模范作用，以优秀共产党员的标准要求自身，不辜负党组织的培养。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">赵任凭指出，学院党总支将以过</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">“政治生日”为契机，引导共产党员时刻铭记自己的“第一身份”和为党工作的“第一职责”，有利于进一步强化党员的身份意识、宗旨意识和责任意识。党员同志们要敢于亮身份，立足本职工作，充分发挥党员在学院事业发展中的积极作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">随后，与会人员纷纷发表感想，表示贾铮老师积极上进、不断进取的工作态度值得大家学习。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"421\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/c5/e2/7b3c65f4443bbc742f43d2e37d51/4fee2721-7ed5-43f7-9576-d2e8bbf0690d.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" data-layer=\"photo\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/c5/e2/7b3c65f4443bbc742f43d2e37d51/4fee2721-7ed5-43f7-9576-d2e8bbf0690d_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'2.jpg\'}\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 421px;\"></p>', '', '2020-11-18 00:00:00', '2020-11-18 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:36:26', '', '2021-04-27 10:44:59', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (160, '信息工程学院组织开展“铸魂育人 立德树人”师德师风建设月系列活动', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">为深入贯彻实施新时代党的教育方针，落实立德树人根本任务，根据《中共盐城师范学院委员会关于开展</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">2020</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">年</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">师德师风建设月</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">主题教育活动的通知》精神，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">11</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">月期间，信息工程学院积极开展</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">铸魂育人 立德树人</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">师德师风建设月系列主题教育活动，深入推进学院教职工师德师风建设。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">从</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">每一支部</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">出发，开展师德师风建设座谈会</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">活动期间，学院充分发挥基层党组织战斗堡垒作用，通过教工第一、第二、第三支部，组织开展师德师风建设月教师座谈会，通过</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">看视频、学文件、说感想</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">三个环节，看模范事迹学先进典型，读文件原件学教师行为规范，立师德、展师风、铸师魂，积极引导广大教师努力成为</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">四有</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">好老师。座谈会上，我院优秀青年教师代表徐华平表示：</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">作为教师，要以生为本，有仁爱之心，坚守党的思想政治教育阵地，守好意识形态底线，培养德智体美劳全面发展的社会主义事业建设者和接班人。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"286\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/b5/28/f59bd66c4376819306eccd02fa82/29a05082-78e2-42cb-be66-5959fa9ce6c5.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'1.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 286px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">从</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">每一教师</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">出发，签订师德师风建设承诺书</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">18</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">日下午，学院组织召开全体教职工大会，会上，学院全体教师认真阅读</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">信息工程学院师德承诺书</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，并郑重签名。活动强调每一位教师同志的责任意识，引导大家反思自己，叩问教育初心。教师们纷纷表示：签订《师德承诺书》，不仅是对自己行为规范的一种约束，同时也是对新时代教育观的进一步理解，要以规范的师德风范投入到教育教学工作中去，认真履行教书育人的职责，为教育作出自己的贡献。</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"701\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/b5/28/f59bd66c4376819306eccd02fa82/57cd4054-ec7d-45d6-81d5-0ec13e66bc09.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'2.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 701px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">从</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">每一学生</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">出发，传递师德师风建设正能量</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">师德师风建设离不开每一位学生的见证与参与。活动中，学院大学生集思广益、组织行动，通过开展</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">老师，我爱您</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">校园角落拍照展、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">挂祝福、赠寄语，对老师说说心里话</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">等主题活动，纷纷送上对老师的美好祝愿，表达对老师的敬爱之意和感激之情。收到祝福，学院教师表示在日后教学过程中要对自己更加高标准、严要求。德高为师，身正为范，要做一名对得起党和国家教育事业的好老师。</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"900\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/b5/28/f59bd66c4376819306eccd02fa82/b03b9585-fe64-4ec1-bf41-72b8647fed01.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'3.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 900px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"524\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/b5/28/f59bd66c4376819306eccd02fa82/9e9af5c8-5de8-4ef8-ab2a-befa76b95a10.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'4.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 524px;\"></p>', '', '2020-11-18 00:00:00', '2020-11-18 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:36:52', '', '2021-04-27 10:44:34', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (161, '信息工程学院第一党支部召开主题党日活动', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">月</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">8</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">日上午</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">信息工程学院第一党支部在学院党员之家召开</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">“谋划‘十四五’、聚力高质量发展”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">主题党日活动</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">。第一支部全体党员同志参加。活动由第一支部书记季芳芳主持。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">与会</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">同志共同学习了</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">《中国共产党十九届五中全会公报》和《习近平谈治国理政》第三卷第十一章</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“用新时代中国特色社会主义思想铸魂育人”选节，深刻领会其丰富内涵和精神实质，并结合本职工作，畅谈“十四五”规划。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">随后</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">第一支部召开师德师风座谈会</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">共同学习</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">《新时代高校教师职业行为十项准则》和《教育部关于高校教师师德失范行为处理的指导意见》等文件精神。并就如何加强师德师德建设等问题展开热烈讨论。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会上</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">季芳芳通报了本周末党总支副书记</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">、副院长姜琳同志将带队走访连云港市赣榆区</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">7</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">个贫困学生家庭，开展支部送温暖等相关活动。</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/4b/85/148193f549aaa9b1c9fe930b7692/1bb78624-ac56-43b7-ab46-e3f1c0df6945.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'1.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/4b/85/148193f549aaa9b1c9fe930b7692/1bb78624-ac56-43b7-ab46-e3f1c0df6945_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p>', '', '2020-11-19 00:00:00', '2020-11-19 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:37:16', '', '2021-04-27 10:44:19', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (162, '学院召开教职工思想政治学习会', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">11月</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">18</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">日下午2:</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">00</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，信息工程学院在学院会议室召开教职工思想政治学习会。全体教职工参加会议，会议由党总支书记赵任凭主持。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 40px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会议</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">传达了校</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">11月份</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">党务工作例会会议精神，</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">通报了文明校园创建工作情况</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">强调了师生意识形态、高校宗教管理、疫情防控等工作。会议对学习党的十九届五中全会精神做了动员部署，要求广大教师在学习文件的同时将自身发展同学校、学院高质量发展新阶段联系起来，做好十四五期间的个人规划。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 40px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会议强调了师德师风建设的重要性，号召全体教职工争做“四有”好老师。全体教师共同观看了第七届全国道德模范提名奖获得者、中国好人、江苏省道德模范、盐城师范学院离休教师包斌、陆一军夫妇和2020“最美教师”、复旦大学张文宏教授感人事迹的视频。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 40px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会议最后，学院全体教师认真阅读“信息工程学院师德承诺书”，并郑重签名，表示自己将以包斌、陆一军夫妇和张文宏教授这些高尚师德的践行者为榜样，以崇高的师德风范投身到教育教学工作中去。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"421\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/9c/45/389dd1ad444dbc0b67a7969b9b66/7a3f08f0-bc95-4ed4-ade4-c0b8998dd5a5.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'4{C@SKLBG$E@K)F$2X$%IP9.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/9c/45/389dd1ad444dbc0b67a7969b9b66/7a3f08f0-bc95-4ed4-ade4-c0b8998dd5a5_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 421px;\"></p>', '', '2020-11-19 00:00:00', '2020-11-19 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:37:42', '', '2021-04-27 10:43:57', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (163, '信息工程学院召开党总支理论中心组（扩大）第八次学习会议', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">11月25日上午9点，信息工程学院党总支在党员之家召开2020年秋学期第八次党总支理论中心组学习会议。本次中心组学习会议接受校巡听组检查，巡听组由校党委副书记、纪委书记刘必清带领，党委宣传部副部长徐晓亮，党委办公室副主任高铭悦，党委宣传部理论宣传教育科科长李荔共同参与。院党总支副书记、院长朱立才，党总支副书记、副院长姜琳，副院长周彩根，科级干部参加会议。会议由党总支书记赵任凭主持。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会上，与会人员共同观看了学习强国视频《党的十九届五中全会精神的逻辑主线》，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">赵任凭</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">领学了《人民日报》系列评论文章《学习</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">“十四五”时期我国发展必须遵循的重要原则、以推动高质量发展为主题和加快构建新发展格局》，传达了校党务工作例会关于学习十九届五中全会的讲话精神的要求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会上，姜琳和周彩根分别联系分管工作，结合学习体会作了重点发言。中心组其他人员也联系自身工作，结合学习内容谈了自己的体会和感想。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议指出，全体中心组成员，一要提高认识，提升政治站位。从讲政治的高度，认识学习重要性，改进学风，坚持学懂弄通做实、真学真信真用，做到内化于心，外化于行。二要查漏补缺，坚持导向引领。要突出事业发展的目标导向，围绕高质量考核指标，进一步对标找差，查漏补缺，做好十三五收官之战，描绘十四五蓝图。三要共谋细化，狠抓工作落实。切实把校党委部署要求、把年度目标任务分解到位、落实到位、责任到位。四要敬业尽责，强化责任担当。要</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">“守好一段渠，种好责任田”，强化“忠诚、干净、担当”的正向激励。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会后，刘必清就巡听情况发表了讲话。刘书记指出，本次学习主题突出，与党的十九届五中全会精神高度契合，会议准备工作到位，材料精心细致，与会人员学习态度端正，交流发言围绕主题、内容详实，强化了理论武装。针对信息工程学院实际提出</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">“三个下功夫”建议：一是要在提高认识上下功夫，深刻理解会议的必要性和重要性，</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">切实增强责任感、紧迫感</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">高度重视理论学习的前瞻性引导作用</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">；二是要在学以致用上下功夫，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">要把学习全会精神作为一条红线贯穿政治学习始终</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">,做到深学、细照、笃行</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">学思践悟</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">结合岗位工作学深学透</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">助力信息工程学院在</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">十四五</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">阶段高质量发展</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">；</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">三是要在示范引领上下功夫</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">学院领导班子和干部要先学一步</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">多学一步</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">学深一步</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">彰显模范带头作用</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，不折不扣地将全会精神落实到学院发展工作中。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/9a/a4/bf068b5a4d7cbe739929054fd1d3/d172e5eb-d4de-4c29-a4b0-ae1e7e9072e8.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p>', '', '2020-11-25 00:00:00', '2020-11-25 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:38:06', '', '2021-04-27 10:43:47', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (164, '信息工程学院召开党支部书记培训会', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">为进一步提升党支部书记履职能力和水平，充分发挥</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">“领头雁”作用，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">12</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: arial; font-size: 20px;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">日下午，信息工程学院在党员之家召开党支部书记培训会。党总支书记赵任凭主持会议。党总支副书记、副院长姜琳，支部书记杨金荣、陈碧云、季芳芳、卞雅妮参加会议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">会上，赵任凭解读了《中国共产党员教育管理工作条例》《中国共产党支部工作条例（试行）》《盐城师范学院</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“党建质量提升年”活动实施方案》等文件精神，强调了线上和线下培训相结合，要求与会同志认真参加盐城师范学院第三期高校基层党务工作者网络培训，保质保量完成学习任务，提升政治理论水平，增强党建工作本领。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会上，赵任凭强调：一是提高政治站位，加强理论</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">学习</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">，要把深入学习宣传贯彻党的十九届五中全会精神作为当前和今后一个时期的重要政治任务，切实加深对全会精神和总书记重要讲话精神的理解把握。围绕学院党建工作全年目标任务，做好支部各项工作。二是强化政治功能，抓好主业主责。坚持党建引领，落实基层党建</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“书记项目”实施，发挥党支部战斗堡垒作用；强化党员教育与管理，加强和改进师德师风建设，落实“立德树人”根本任务；健全支部组织设置，认真学习</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">《中国共产党基层组织选举工作条例</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">》，为换届工作做好准备。三是拓展工作思路，丰富党日活动形式和内容，推进优质党支部建设，增强基层党组织政治功能和组织力，努力实现党建工作和业务工作</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“双提升”。</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/79/86/4bedbba8419697d6030bf5c40a85/33ba2968-0846-4873-b2e3-ee4ecc473ec0.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'1.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/79/86/4bedbba8419697d6030bf5c40a85/33ba2968-0846-4873-b2e3-ee4ecc473ec0_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p>', '', '2020-12-03 00:00:00', '2020-12-03 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:38:32', '', '2021-04-27 10:43:25', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (165, '铭记历史，致敬英雄信息工程学院组织集中观看大型纪录片《为了和平》', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">为深入贯彻落实习近平总书记在纪念中国人民志愿军抗美援朝出国作战</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">70周年大会上的重要讲话精神，深入开展“四史”学习教育，大力弘扬伟大的抗美援朝精神，加强新时代爱国主义教育，</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">12月3日下午，信息工程学院在会议室组织全体教职工集中观看</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">大型电视纪录片《为了和平》</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">。活动由</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">党总支副书记、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">院长朱立才主持。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">纪录片共有</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">6集，分别为《正义担当》《殊死较量》《血性迸发》《英雄赞歌》《万众一心》《伟大胜利》，采取史论结合、故事表达的方式，深入反映伟大的抗美援朝精神的丰富内涵和时代价值，集中展示了中国人民志愿军的英雄事迹和革命精神。根据学院制定的</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">观看学习与座谈研讨方案</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，本次观看纪录片第一集《正义担当》。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">通过对纪录片的学习，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">全体教职工热血澎湃，深刻感受了党和政府领导人以非凡气魄和胆略作出抗美援朝、保家卫国的历史性决策，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">纷纷表示要继承和发扬</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">伟大</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">抗美援朝精神，以习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想为指引，思想铸魂</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">立德树人</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">为实现中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦而培育英才</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/1d/de/b62da90e4ab2ba5da3c9a6316f39/fd0c9a9d-0461-49d3-8f1f-3f0fe3a24b20.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'图片1.png\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/1d/de/b62da90e4ab2ba5da3c9a6316f39/fd0c9a9d-0461-49d3-8f1f-3f0fe3a24b20_d.png\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/1d/de/b62da90e4ab2ba5da3c9a6316f39/ef6c01f4-74e8-4e2c-aa9c-30e666c013e2.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'图片2.png\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/1d/de/b62da90e4ab2ba5da3c9a6316f39/ef6c01f4-74e8-4e2c-aa9c-30e666c013e2_d.png\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p>', '', '2020-12-05 00:00:00', '2020-12-05 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:38:56', '', '2021-04-27 13:23:40', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (166, '信息工程学院开展“请回答，1848”——大学生“青马工程”系列讲堂', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">12月4日下午，信息工程学院在学院会议室</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">举办</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">“请回答，1848”——大学生“青马工程”系列讲堂</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">活动</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">活动</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">邀请信息工程学院原党总支书记、关工委成员梁建林主讲，党总支副书记、副院长姜琳和学生党员、发展对象代表参加。党总支书记赵任凭主持</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">活动</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">梁建林结合马克思的成长经历和社会主义发展史，为大家</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">认真讲读了</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">《</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">共产党宣言</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">》。他鼓励青年大学生要进一步坚定理想信念、练就过硬本领、投身强国伟业，努力成长为新时代合格的青年马克思主义者，为中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦不懈奋斗。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">在现场，梁书记还向大家展示了他</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">17岁时学习使用的，一直珍藏的1977年版的《共产党宣言》。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">活动中，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">赵任凭领学了《共产党宣言》节选。他指出，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">《共产党宣言》是马克思主义诞生的标志，为历代共产党人确立初心，是引领历代共产党人奋斗前行的精神路标。希望全体同学</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">在读原著、悟原理中践行夯实理论基础，在学思践悟中坚定理想信念，在奋发有为中践行初心使命，努力成为合格的社会主义建设者和接班人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">随后，在场</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">的</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">同学</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">们</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">展开了热烈的讨论，交流了自己的学习心得。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">182班刘琦同学表示：“本次讲堂，加深了我对马克思主义的理解，明确了学生党员和学生干部的责任与担当。我将</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">以</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">习近平</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">总书记</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">对青年大学生的要求为目标</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">勇于</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">承担</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">起新</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">时代赋予的</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">使命</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，在奋斗中绽放青春的光芒！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">据悉，信息工程学院青马工程班还将陆续以班级、支部、学习小组为单位开展经典原著研读、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">“四史”教育、理论宣讲等系列活动，引导青马学员感受马克思主义理论魅力，培养马克思主义理论思维，做新时代的青年马克思主义者。</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"577\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/5c/d7/3e08927849d78d05662be77d8cdc/bc044ce9-74db-4e31-b328-9e063f3fd13a.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'QQ图片20201206191954.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 577px;\"></p>', '', '2020-12-06 00:00:00', '2020-12-06 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:39:18', '', '2021-04-27 13:23:18', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (167, '学院召开2020年秋学期第十次党总支理论学习中心组（扩大）学习会', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">12月16日上午，信息工程学院党总支在党员之家召开理论学习中心组（扩大）学习会，开展专题廉政教育。学院领导班子全体成员，各支部书记参会。会议由党总支书记赵任凭主持。</span></p><h3 align=\"justify\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(43, 88, 155); margin: 5px 0em; font-size: 16px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">与会人员共同学习校纪委《关于开展党风廉政建设责任制落实情况检查考核的通知》《关于开展2020年度二级党组织书记、纪检委员述责述廉工作的通知》精神。共同学习了《高校违反师德师风典型案例（二）》《“天网行动”典型案例》。</span></h3><h3 align=\"justify\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(43, 88, 155); margin: 5px 0em; font-size: 16px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议指出，</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">党风廉政建设</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">工作是我们党的建设的重要方面，与会人员要自省自警自律，增强拒腐防变的能力，驰而不息正风肃纪，坚定不移反腐惩恶。</span></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议要求，一要加强作风建设，充分认识作风建设的重要性和迫切性，持续深化“不忘初心，牢记使命”主题教育；二要加强师德师风建设，坚决杜绝师德不端、学术不端等行为，齐心建立一支高素质的教师队伍。三要</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">落实主体责任</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，严格</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">履行“一岗双责”</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">推动全面从严治党向纵深发展</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，为学院十四五规划工作提供坚强的政治保障、组织保障和纪律保障。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会上</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，赵任凭与班子成员及支部书记签订了</span><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">《</span></span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">廉政建设责任书</span><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">》。</span><br></span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/b1/0e/786b6801465b83e836c0477219d9/2399c3b5-a0d1-453c-a58d-343f49544b13.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" data-layer=\"photo\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/b1/0e/786b6801465b83e836c0477219d9/2399c3b5-a0d1-453c-a58d-343f49544b13_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'QQ图片20201217164149.jpg\'}\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/b1/0e/786b6801465b83e836c0477219d9/8a7456f8-2b8e-4f2a-88ec-e7025926396a.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" data-layer=\"photo\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/b1/0e/786b6801465b83e836c0477219d9/8a7456f8-2b8e-4f2a-88ec-e7025926396a_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'2.jpg\'}\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"421\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/b1/0e/786b6801465b83e836c0477219d9/b9e51e6b-5679-448f-acba-789a45d5c38d.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" data-layer=\"photo\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/b1/0e/786b6801465b83e836c0477219d9/b9e51e6b-5679-448f-acba-789a45d5c38d_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'3.jpg\'}\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 421px;\"><br></p>', '', '2020-12-17 00:00:00', '2020-12-17 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:39:47', '', '2021-04-27 13:23:07', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (168, '信息工程学院开展“过政治生日、忆入党初心”活动', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">12</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">23</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">9</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">点，信息工程学院党总支在学院党员之家开展“过政治生日、忆入党初心”活动。学院党总支副书记、院长朱立才，党总支副书记、副院长姜琳，副院长周彩根以及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">7</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">12</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">月份入党的教师党员参加会议，第一党支部全体党员列席会议。会议由党总支书记赵任凭主持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">活动伊始，参会人员全体起立，奏唱国际歌。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">活动中，朱立才给过政治生日的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">7</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">名同志赠送政治生日贺卡。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">7</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; line-height: 1.5em;\">名党员同志深情回顾了入党经历和政治成长心路历程。大家一起忆初心、话使命、谈今日，展未来。纷纷表示，收到属于自己的政治生日贺卡，心情特别激动，切实感受到党组织的关心和爱护。活动中，其他同志也畅谈了自己的感悟。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">活动最后，赵任凭代表党总支祝贺同志们政治生日快乐，感谢他们在学院发展中的付出。同时，提出三点希望：一是希望大家深化对“政治生日”活动意义的认识，自觉提升自己身份意识，要有党员的觉悟和品德；二是希望大家更加坚定理想信念，不忘立德树人使命，要有党员的素养和能力；三是要以饱满的热情投入到学院和学校高质量发展的事业中，在学院十四五工作中充分发挥模范带头作用，要有党员的担当和作为。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/d9/81/7011e43944f797efdf42eb2d9fc8/abeb8d80-4d3f-487a-97e8-42fa17a38095.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/d9/81/7011e43944f797efdf42eb2d9fc8/abeb8d80-4d3f-487a-97e8-42fa17a38095_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'111.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"450\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 450px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/d9/81/7011e43944f797efdf42eb2d9fc8/b89a9efe-85f0-49bd-9502-63491a7fba05.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/d9/81/7011e43944f797efdf42eb2d9fc8/b89a9efe-85f0-49bd-9502-63491a7fba05_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'222.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"450\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 450px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/d9/81/7011e43944f797efdf42eb2d9fc8/cdc3c1f4-8890-4b40-807b-221907def0d0.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/d9/81/7011e43944f797efdf42eb2d9fc8/cdc3c1f4-8890-4b40-807b-221907def0d0_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'333.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"450\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 450px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>', '', '2020-12-23 00:00:00', '2020-12-23 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:40:39', '', '2021-04-27 13:22:47', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (169, '信息工程学院第一党支部举行主题党日活动', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">23</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">日，信息工程学院第一党支部在党员之家举行“规范基层党建</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">规范换届工作”主题党日活动。活动由第一党支部书记季芳芳主持。第一党支部全体同志参加会议。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">季芳芳领学了习近平总书记视察江苏重要讲话指示精神、党的十九届五中全会精神（节选）和《习近平谈治国理政》第三卷第八专题《增强忧患意识，防范化解风险挑战》（节选），重点学习了《中国共产党基层组织选举工作条例》，并观看了系列微动漫。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">会议强调，基层党组织换届是党内重要政治性工作，对于发扬党内民主、尊重和保障党员民主权利，增强基层党组织政治功能和组织力具有重要意义。全体同志要真正将《中国共产党基层组织选举工作条例》内容学懂悟透，切实保证换届工作顺利完成。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/0c/ec/0ce0c4f04e429082a343ece44514/84880c90-c9e6-4f99-8b61-09702c965c2e.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/0c/ec/0ce0c4f04e429082a343ece44514/84880c90-c9e6-4f99-8b61-09702c965c2e_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'12.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"400\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 400px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/0c/ec/0ce0c4f04e429082a343ece44514/2af435d9-6e05-4046-91d3-482c6f43b397.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/0c/ec/0ce0c4f04e429082a343ece44514/2af435d9-6e05-4046-91d3-482c6f43b397_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'13.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"400\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 400px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/0c/ec/0ce0c4f04e429082a343ece44514/4a5dea09-83ee-4e92-9eb3-3109bb420654.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/0c/ec/0ce0c4f04e429082a343ece44514/4a5dea09-83ee-4e92-9eb3-3109bb420654_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'14.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"400\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 400px;\"></p>', '', '2020-12-25 00:00:00', '2020-12-25 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:41:14', '', '2021-04-27 13:22:26', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (170, '学院召开2020年度教职工考核工作部署会', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 43px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">2021</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">分，信息工程学院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">年度教职工考核工作部署会在党员之家召开。学院党总支副书记、院长朱立才，党总支副书记、副院长姜琳，副院长周彩根，各系部负责人及相关工作人员参加会议，会议由党总支书记赵任凭主持。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 43px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">会议对学校</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">年度教职工考核办法作了解读，强调了考核工作的要求，明确了各系部的推优比例，并对考核任务分工、考核时间安排、考核方式方法、考核结果评定等重点内容进行明确部署和具体说明。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 43px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">会议要求，各系部一是要在思想上认识到位，各系部要把这项涉及教职工切身利益的工作重视起来，确保发挥年终考核工作的杠杆和激励作用。二是要在行动上落实到位，年终考核工作时间紧、任务重，各系部要认真筹划、妥善安排，按时间节点完成相应工作，保证学院整体工作的顺利进行。三是要在结果上公平到位。各系部要认真了解每位老师一年的工作情况和所取得的工作实绩，要客观公正地评价每位老师，要把真正优秀的教师推出来，充分发挥年终考核的导向功能，调动教职工工作的积极性、主动性和创造性。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 43px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/c8/87/3ede0cda4a46ad985bfa86590cb0/b6d87f42-f201-4267-9f37-ed34164d44d4.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/c8/87/3ede0cda4a46ad985bfa86590cb0/b6d87f42-f201-4267-9f37-ed34164d44d4_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'222.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"400\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 400px;\"></p>', '', '2021-01-07 00:00:00', '2021-01-07 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:41:38', '', '2021-04-27 13:22:13', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (171, '“送‘福’进宿舍，暖冬心连‘信’”——信息工程学院学生党员为身边同学办实事', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">1月1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">0</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日下午，信息工程学院</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">学生党支部</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">团总支</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">组织学生党员、学生团干，深入外省籍、少数民族学生宿舍，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">送</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">‘</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">福</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">’</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">进宿舍，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">为生办实事，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">暖冬心连</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">‘</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">信</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">’</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">下午两点，学生党员、团干组成志愿服务小分队，兵分三路，深入外省籍、少数民族学生宿舍，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">向同学们表达问候和祝福</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，帮助他们打扫宿舍卫生，协助排查安全隐患，和他们一起聊聊天、拉家常，提醒他们疫情反复，注意出行安全，少出门、戴口罩、勤洗手。随后，志愿者送上准备好的新春对联和“福”字，帮助他们贴上宿舍门框，为生办实事，送福送到家。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">面对</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">志愿者们</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">热情的祝福，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">同学们</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">表示</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">在严寒的冬日感受到了学院大家庭的温暖，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">纷纷</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">表达</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">感谢，合影留念。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">学生党员史梦香：“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">送</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">‘福’字进宿舍</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">活动</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">是我们学生党员为身边同学服务、为大家办实事的一小步，我们</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">为</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">外省籍、少数民族</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">同学们送去新春祝福</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">、温暖和关怀，帮助他们打扫卫生的</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">同时，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">也提醒大家</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">安全离校，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">为</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">推动</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">宿舍</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">文明建设，创造整洁、文明、舒适、优美、规范的</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">校园</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">生活环境</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">提供自己的一份力量</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">后续我们将继续发光发热，在学院的统一指导下，开展系列为生办实事活动，结合身边同学的实际需要发挥党员先锋作用。”</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/e1/14/4f81b1ab41b1b75cbe421a153676/050e0c05-d551-4186-9134-7a38d79d020f.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'图片1.png\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/e1/14/4f81b1ab41b1b75cbe421a153676/050e0c05-d551-4186-9134-7a38d79d020f_d.png\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"424\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/e1/14/4f81b1ab41b1b75cbe421a153676/aaae3263-3551-44af-b84d-b06fe7034d76.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'图片2.png\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/e1/14/4f81b1ab41b1b75cbe421a153676/aaae3263-3551-44af-b84d-b06fe7034d76_d.png\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 424px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"421\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/e1/14/4f81b1ab41b1b75cbe421a153676/42cadaa6-9605-4e70-8de3-6dd8fb0da597.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'图片3.png\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/e1/14/4f81b1ab41b1b75cbe421a153676/42cadaa6-9605-4e70-8de3-6dd8fb0da597_d.png\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 421px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p>', '', '2021-01-12 00:00:00', '2021-01-12 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:42:02', '', '2021-04-27 13:22:00', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (172, '信息工程学院召开意识形态工作讨论会', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">1月2</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">9</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">日下午，信息工程学院在学院党员之家召开意识形态工作讨论会。学院党委副书记、副院长姜琳和全体辅导员参加会议。会议由学院党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会上，各辅导员根据学校意识形态工作督查内容和责任分工，将近三年来意识形态工作进行梳理，相关材料进行归档；就新学期意识形态工作的开展提出建议并充分讨论。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会议充分肯定了学院近三年的意识形态工作，会议强调，在新形势下做好意识形态工作具有极端重要性，学院要加强党对意识形态工作的全面领导，严格落实意识形态工作责任制，牢牢掌握意识形态工作的主动权，营造风清气正的政治生态和良好的育人环境。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会议还对寒假期间疫情防控工作进行了再部署。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/7c/8c/851ee5b94792956e6f443dc7760e/72f668af-9e0b-49f0-b870-203e23c6cd21.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'图片1.png\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/7c/8c/851ee5b94792956e6f443dc7760e/72f668af-9e0b-49f0-b870-203e23c6cd21_d.png\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p>', '', '2021-01-30 00:00:00', '2021-01-30 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:42:28', '', '2021-04-27 13:21:48', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (173, '信息工程学院召开春学期第一次支部书记会议', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">日下午，信息工程学院于党员之家召开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">年春学期开学第一次支部书记会议，党委书记赵任凭，党委副书记、副院长姜琳，</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">党委委员徐贵伍</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">以及全体支部书记参加会议。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">各支部书记围绕“书记项目”、“书记工作室”和“优质党支部”项目建设</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">,</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">汇报进展、交流经验，谋划学期党建工作新思路、求实效、出成绩，积极向建党一百周年献礼。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">赵任凭充分肯定了各支部工作，并要求：一是坚持政治统领，全面推进学院高质量发展，各支部要全力以赴，积极参与国家一流专业建设和工程教育专业论证等学院中心工作，实现党建工作与业务工作双提升。二是认真开展好党史学习教育，各支部要积极开展多种形式学习活动，认真学习贯彻习近平总书记重要讲话精神，从党的百年伟大奋斗历程中汲取继续前进的智慧和力量。三是加强支部组织建设，严格执行各项规章制度，</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">切实履行“</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">一岗双责</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">”</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em;\">，落实内控机制，“三会一课”制度，党员密切联系师生制度，利用学院“智慧党建”平台，开展“学习强国”平台学习竞赛月活动，调动广大师生党员积极性，充分发挥党支部战斗堡垒作用。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/b7/e2/3d5dd9324de6a4eeacf017808a1b/483ac196-d29f-4a6a-b5f7-4437015150f0.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/b7/e2/3d5dd9324de6a4eeacf017808a1b/483ac196-d29f-4a6a-b5f7-4437015150f0_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'37.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\"></p>', '', '2021-03-06 00:00:00', '2021-03-06 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:42:50', '', '2021-04-27 13:20:37', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (174, '信息工程学院召开“智慧党建”平台优化工作研讨会', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">日，信息工程学院“智慧党建”平台优化工作研讨会于党员之家召开。党委书记赵任凭主持会议，平台建设工作负责教师季芳芳、徐华平、贾铮和相关学生参加会议。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">技术人员进行现场展示，与会人员听取智慧党建平台建设情况汇报。技术指导老师提出继续完善前端页面设计、巩固后端数据库信息、做好技术维护等合理化建议。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">赵任凭强调要加快平台的建设，强化平台安全工作，进一步明确分工，特别是平台维护人员的职责，并提出四点要求：一是提升政治意识，加强综合平台的研发工作，拓展功能；二是提升安全意识，平台作为意识形态的重要阵地，要高度重视平台安全维护工作；三是提升思想意识，建好用好平台，保证在维护人员变动情况下，阵地不变、效果不减；四是提升纪律意识，全体人员都要严守纪律，严肃认真地开展工作。</span></p>', '', '2021-03-06 00:00:00', '2021-03-06 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:43:12', '', '2021-04-27 10:47:27', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (175, '信息工程学院师生热议2021年“全国”两会精神', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">日、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">日，全国政协十三届四次会议、十三届全国人大四次会议先后在北京开幕。信息工程学院积极组织广大师生收听收看两会报道，关注会议盛况，掌握“两会”热点，热议</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">2021</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">年全国“两会”精神。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/41/c9/2793428c4da6b3ce66a007de3724/385610f2-17b9-4428-a309-772d20af4ec3.png\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'999.png\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"431\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 431px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">院党委委员、教工第一支部书记季芳芳说：“两会的召开振奋人心，催人奋进！我们要时刻关注两会进程、了解两会动态，作为一名基层党务工作者和高校辅导员，我感到由衷的骄傲和自豪！中国始终同国际社会齐心协力抗击疫情，展示了负责任大国的责任担当，中国在世界政治经济舞台上的影响越来越大，我将进一步加强政治理论学习，认真做好本职工作，积极投身学校学院事业高质量发展建设中，为伟大祖国早日实现中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦贡献自己的力量。”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">学生党员刘梦园说：“迈过极不平凡的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">年，踏上全面建设社会主义现代化国家新征程。我们是未来祖国建设的中坚力量，我将认真学习贯彻“两会”精神，坚定理想信念跟党走，德智体美劳全面发展，发挥自身专业优势，积极投身建设，为学院发展作贡献，为社会奉献青春力量。”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">全国“两会”如期召开，为我国迈向第二个百年奋斗目标开了一个好头。站在‘十四五’开局新起点上，信息工程学院党委将以习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想为指导，</span><span style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">凝心聚力，砥砺奋进，深入贯彻新发展理念，加快融入新发展格局，锐意改革创新，强化责任担当，进一步优化学科专业结构，以软件工程国家一流专业建设为中心，推进软件工程专业工程教育专业认证标志性工作，加快实现高质量发展！</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/41/c9/2793428c4da6b3ce66a007de3724/da2c1fc7-d24a-4471-8364-c98981e0cca1.png\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/41/c9/2793428c4da6b3ce66a007de3724/da2c1fc7-d24a-4471-8364-c98981e0cca1_d.png\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'998.png\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"223\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 223px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-03-06 00:00:00', '2021-03-06 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:43:37', '', '2021-04-27 09:49:21', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (176, '信息工程学院开展“学党史、悟思想、办实事、开新局”主题党日活动', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">日下午，信息工程学院党委组织全体教工党员在盐城新四军纪念馆开展“学党史、悟思想、办实事、开新局”主题党日活动。院党委书记赵任凭，党委副书记、院长朱立才，党委副书记、副院长姜琳，副院长周彩根和全体教工党员参加活动。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">纪念馆由“民族危急</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">铁军诞生”“抗日战旗</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">遍插华中”“重建军部</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">浴火重生”“兵民鏖战</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">坚持敌后”“战胜困难</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">建设根据地”“局部反攻</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">扩大解放区”“走向胜利</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">铸造辉煌”等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">个展厅组成。一件件文物，一张张照片，伴着解说员深情的话语，为我们展开了新四军那艰苦而辉煌的历史画卷。正如新四军军歌所唱“东进，东进，我们是铁的新四军。”铁军精神的丰富内涵深深地震撼了每一位同志的心灵。在党旗下，全体同志高举右手，神情肃穆，重温入党誓词，再悟初心使命。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">赵任凭表示：“在‘两个一百年’奋斗目标历史交汇的关键节点，学院党委组织全体党员参观新四军纪念馆，开展党史学习主题活动，正当其时，十分必要。信息工程学院党委将以铁军精神为引领，以‘铁军班’建设为抓手，落实立德树人根本任务，发扬‘拓荒牛’‘孺子牛’‘老黄牛’的‘三牛’精神，出实招，办实事，开辟学院高质量发展新局面。”</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">据悉，信息工程学院党委将策划系列活动，开展党史学习教育，推进学校学院事业发展，以实际行动向建党一百周年献礼。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/3c/9b/135c4061433f88d2759d3c39c3d8/fe754487-a475-4d77-969c-c8236457604f.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/3c/9b/135c4061433f88d2759d3c39c3d8/fe754487-a475-4d77-969c-c8236457604f_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'45.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/3c/9b/135c4061433f88d2759d3c39c3d8/da2c524e-dd35-4512-8e99-d8dcda2319b1.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/3c/9b/135c4061433f88d2759d3c39c3d8/da2c524e-dd35-4512-8e99-d8dcda2319b1_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'46.JPG\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/3c/9b/135c4061433f88d2759d3c39c3d8/ef5374cd-f0bd-4649-a846-3e1683d64654.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/3c/9b/135c4061433f88d2759d3c39c3d8/ef5374cd-f0bd-4649-a846-3e1683d64654_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'677.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-03-07 00:00:00', '2021-03-07 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:44:04', '', '2021-04-27 09:49:29', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (177, '信息工程学院组织开展庆祝“三八”国际妇女节主题活动', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 56px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">8</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">日上午，信息工程学院在党员之家组织开展庆祝“三八”国际妇女节主题活动，向学院全体女同志致以节日的祝福。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><br><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">学院工会精心策划，形式新颖，女教职工们积极参与，乐在其中。活动期间，院党委书记赵任凭、院长朱立才、工会主席姜琳代表学院向全体女教职工分发节日礼品，并致以节日的问候，感谢她们立足岗位，奋勇争先，为学院的发展作出贡献。女教职工们相互关心，交流谈心，分享教学经验，同时也表达了对学院的感激之情。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><br><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">活动的开展愉悦了教职工的心情，丰富了教职工精神生活，加强了情感交流，进一步增强了团队凝聚力和向心力，激励女同胞们继续发扬“巾帼不让须眉”之势</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">用高度的责任心和敬业情操</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\">在自平凡的岗位上挥洒着辛劳和汗水，以更加饱满的热情投入到新学期的工作中来。</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"271\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/42/09/91960a8941c7a24fac53adc7de42/170986e4-1368-4dac-8857-2912b26dabbd.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'06E_MIN_]B__~0N@EAC_8{L.png\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/42/09/91960a8941c7a24fac53adc7de42/170986e4-1368-4dac-8857-2912b26dabbd_d.png\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 271px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/42/09/91960a8941c7a24fac53adc7de42/2694952e-0cdd-45f1-9b76-1280795d71c6.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'}OUMEQKD6EFTKEU[Y}U4S1W.png\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/42/09/91960a8941c7a24fac53adc7de42/2694952e-0cdd-45f1-9b76-1280795d71c6_d.png\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 267px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 56px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 20px;\"></span></span><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-03-08 00:00:00', '2021-03-08 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:44:25', '', '2021-04-27 09:49:36', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (178, '信息工程学院召开巡视材料工作部署会', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">3</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">9</span>日下午，信息工程学院在学院党员之家召开省委巡视工作材料部署会。学院党委副书记、院长朱立才，副院长周彩根，党委委员、办公室主任徐贵伍，学工办主任季芳芳和相关工作人员参加会议。会议由学院党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会议对学校</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">关于校巡视工作材料组的通知内容</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">作了解读。强调了巡视工作要求，确定了学院材料组人员名单，明确了各自的责任分工。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会议强调，本次省委巡视工作是对我校全面工作的一次“政治体检”，巡视工作会有力地推动学校学院各项事业的高质量发展。全院人员要以高度的自觉性和坚定的责任心积极参与到巡视工作中，高质量完成材料的整理工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会议要求全体人员：一要提高认识，坚决落实学校关于巡视工作决策部署，高标准、高质量地完成学校下达的各项巡视工作任务；二要严格对照学校要求，对近三年工作的各项资料再梳理、再完善、再审核、再把关，查漏补缺，切实做到全面、及时、准确、实事求是地整理和提交各类材料；三要以巡视工作为契机，统一思想、振奋精神、寻找差距、理清思路、做到配合巡视和抓好日常工作两不误，两促进，全力推进学院各项工作深入落实。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"346\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/3c/13/0655d2d44e938972804f6bf5c5c0/7cab9d1f-1030-4e1d-a46b-a74893ff6741.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'IMG_20210309_154508.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/3c/13/0655d2d44e938972804f6bf5c5c0/7cab9d1f-1030-4e1d-a46b-a74893ff6741_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 346px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"></span><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-03-10 00:00:00', '2021-03-10 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:44:49', '', '2021-04-27 09:49:42', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (179, '学院召开2021年第一次党委理论学习中心组（扩大）学习会', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">3</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">10</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日上午，信息工程学院党委在党员之家召开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">2021</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">年第一次党委理论学习中心组（扩大）学习会，集体学习了党章党规以及关于巡视工作的文件精神。学院领导班子、各支部书记以及科级干部参加学习。会议由院党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">与会人员共同学习了党的十八大以来习近平总书记关于党章党规的重要论述和关于巡视工作的重要论述以及《江苏省委关于贯彻</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">&lt;</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">中国共产党巡视工作条例</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">实施办法》中关于巡视范围和内容、巡视工作方式和权限、巡视工作程序等内容，会上还集中观看了有关党的巡视巡察制度的十九大党章公开课。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议指出，巡视制度是党章规定的一项重要制度，是落实党要管党、从严治党要求的重要手段，也是强化党内监督的重要形式。</span><a name=\"OLE_LINK13\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183);\"></a><a name=\"OLE_LINK14\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 122, 183);\"></a></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议要求</span></span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">：一要统一思想、提高站位、积极配合校巡视各项工作，增强“四个意识”，切实做到“两个维护”；二要努力提高接受监督的自觉性和坚定性，充分发挥巡视的“政治体检”作用，发现工作不足，主动整改；三要以巡视工作为契机，树标立杆，对标找差，全方位推动学院十四五开局之年的事业高质量发展，以优异成绩迎接建党一百周年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-03-10 00:00:00', '2021-03-10 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:45:10', '', '2021-04-27 09:49:48', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (180, '信息工程学院召开省委巡视工作动员部署会', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 47px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">12</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日下午，信息工程学院于学院会议室召开省委巡视工作动员部署会。学院领导班子成员，全体教职工参加会议。会议由院党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会上传达了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">8</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日学校全面从严治党工作会议和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">12</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日上午省委巡视组巡视盐城师范学院党委工作动员会会议精神。着重传达了省委巡视组组长陈容桂和学校党委书记戴斌荣的讲话精神。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议要求，全体教师一要统一思想，提高站位，深刻认识巡视工作的重要意义，自觉增强“四个意识”，切实做到“两个维护”。巡视工作是难得的机遇，全体教师要自觉把握好，不能错过；二要积极配合，认真参与，注重在行动上体现政治素养，提升接受监督的自觉性和坚定性，巡视工作是一项政治任务，配合巡视是全体教师的政治责任，不能推卸。三是要以生为本，积极工作，努力在工作细节上展现政治品格，全体教师要对照“四有”好老师标准，以立德树人为己任，树立以学生为中心的理念，突出教学工作的中心地位。巡视工作是全员之责，参与巡视是全体教师应尽之责，不能旁观。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议强调，巡视工作已经开始，巡视没有局外人，巡视过程就是对学校学院和全体教师在贯彻落实习近平总书记关于高等教育发展的重要论述和党中央关于新时代高等教育教育教学改革决策部署，所做各项工作和付出全部努力的检阅和审视。全院师生要同心协力，积极配合，努力在省委巡视工作过程中，展示信工人的风采、作信工人的贡献，以实际行动向建党</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">100</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">周年献礼！</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"359\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/28/19/27e8fd5846b1a77a0a397311ffcb/d9899b28-b7a6-4118-903d-1b1d3f4b51bb.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'动员部署会1.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/28/19/27e8fd5846b1a77a0a397311ffcb/d9899b28-b7a6-4118-903d-1b1d3f4b51bb_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 359px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"359\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/28/19/27e8fd5846b1a77a0a397311ffcb/34c95434-82b8-4812-8cd7-a3f2d4a25a65.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'动员部署会2.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/28/19/27e8fd5846b1a77a0a397311ffcb/34c95434-82b8-4812-8cd7-a3f2d4a25a65_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 359px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\"></span></span><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-03-13 00:00:00', '2021-03-13 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:45:35', '', '2021-04-27 09:44:15', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (181, '信息工程学院召开2021年春学期教职工第一次政治理论学习会', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">12</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日下午，信息工程学院在学院会议室召开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">2021</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">年春学期教职工第一次政治理论学习会。学院领导班子成员，全体教职工参加会议。会议由院党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会上，全体教职工观看十九大党章公开课第十八讲《党的巡视巡察制度》视频，学习领悟巡视与巡察制度的概念、重要意义。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议结合江苏省委落实巡视条例的实施办法，对省委巡视组巡视工作内容及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">13</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">种巡视方式作了解读，并对省委第六巡视组在我校巡视期间的主要巡视内容作出简要说明。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议指出，巡视工作是对落实全面从严治党主体责任和监督责任进行监督，着重发现党的纪律问题及学校学院党委贯彻落实党中央关于新时代高等教育的决策部署、政策文件落实情况，对学校学院现行各项工作开展情况的一次全面“政治体检”，通过巡视，必然推动学校学院各项事业健康发展，为高质量发展提供政治基础和保障。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"359\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/6b/a6/592bc0834c188a22bcc9afc6dfe6/9a3e0317-d385-420c-9cc8-cf4ef474f078.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'学习会1.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/6b/a6/592bc0834c188a22bcc9afc6dfe6/9a3e0317-d385-420c-9cc8-cf4ef474f078_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 359px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"359\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/6b/a6/592bc0834c188a22bcc9afc6dfe6/7989fd79-bf37-47e7-9fa8-d707855891c2.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'学习会2.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/6b/a6/592bc0834c188a22bcc9afc6dfe6/7989fd79-bf37-47e7-9fa8-d707855891c2_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 359px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\"></span><br></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-03-13 00:00:00', '2021-03-13 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:46:03', '', '2021-04-27 09:44:08', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (182, '信息工程学院开展“过政治生日、忆入党初心”活动', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">2021</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">3</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">17</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">9</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">点，信息工程学院党委在学院党员之家开展“过政治生日、忆入党初心”活动。学院党委书记赵任凭、党委副书记、院长朱立才，党委副书记、副院长姜琳，副院长周彩根以及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">10</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">1</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">月至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">3</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">月份入党的教师党员参加了会议，第一党支部全体党员列席会议。会议由党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">活动伊始，参会人员全体起立，奏唱国际歌。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">党委书记赵任凭给朱立才等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">10</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">名党员颁发了“不忘初心，牢记使命”政治生日纪念卡，并和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">10</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">名党员合影。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">10</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">名党员同志深情回顾了入党经历和政治成长心路历程。纷纷表示，收到属于自己的政治生日贺卡，心情特别激动，切实感受到党组织的关心和爱护。一定要珍惜工作岗位活动中，好好工作，全力以赴培养学生。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 40px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">党委副书记、院长朱立才做了生日感言发言，朱院长简单回顾了其入党经过和工作经历，重点提出一是要点亮身份，做表率，发挥党员模范带头作用，认真培养学生；二是牢记使命，勤奋工作，要基于国产软件、硬件开展教学研究工作，服务师生，争取“十四五”学院工作取得巨大进步。会上，其他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">9</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">位同志也畅谈了自己的感悟，做了表态发言。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;活动最后，党委书记赵任凭要求党员不忘初心、牢记使命、奋发有为，切实增强荣誉感、责任感、使命感，争做“四讲四有”党员，充分发挥先锋模范作用，增强基层党组织的创造力、凝聚力、战斗力，还对对疫情期间广大党员所做的工作高度评价。同时提出三点希望：一是希望大家深化对“政治生日”活动意义的认识，自觉提升自己身份意识，要有党员的觉悟和品德；二是希望大家更加坚定理想信念，不忘立德树人使命，要有党员的素养和能力；三是要以饱满的热情投入到学院和学校高质量发展的事业中，在学院十四五工作中充分发挥模范带头作用，要有党员的担当和作为。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/95/6a/44e992af412198f6c70d10d146ef/1e5b732b-dc93-4a35-ac73-fd3576649207.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'QQ图片20210317151004.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/95/6a/44e992af412198f6c70d10d146ef/1e5b732b-dc93-4a35-ac73-fd3576649207_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-03-17 00:00:00', '2021-03-17 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:46:28', '', '2021-04-27 09:44:01', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (183, '信息工程学院开展2021年全国 “两会”精神专题学习', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">3</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">24</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em;\">日下午，信息工程学院在学院会议室召开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">2021</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em;\">年全国“两会”精神专题学习会。学院领导班子成员，全体教职工参加会议。会议由院党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em;\">会上，赵任凭向全体教师传达了全省教育系统传达学习</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">2021</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em;\">年全国“两会”精神报告会的内容，领学了《全国人大代表和专家解读</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">--</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em;\">政府工作报告教育内容修改透露了什么》《十四五规划和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">2035</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em;\">年远景目标纲要提出建设高质量教育体系》。重点解读了政府工作报告中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">10</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em;\">处涉及教育的修改内容。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会议指出，政府工作报告修改之处，体现以人民为中心和教育新发展理念；两处修改涉及高校，强调学科结构优化、区域均衡及提升服务经济社会能力；三处修改涉及教师，在高质量教育体系建设关键点发力，强调建设高素质专业化教师队伍、倡导全社会尊师重教和加强师德师风建设；增加了“加强县域高中建设”、事关乡村振兴和经济社会发展大局；增加了“在线教育和终身学习”、推进学习型社会建设；增加了“规范校外培训”、营造健康教育生态；增加了“强化全民国防教育”，凸显总体国家安全观。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">会议强调，认真学习贯彻落实全国“两会”精神是当前一项重要的政治任务，要按照省委统一部署和学校党委通知要求，学懂弄通、学深悟透，切实把思想和行动统一到“两会”精神上来，密切联系实际工作，坚决把各项决策部署细化实化，加强师德师风建设，努力建设一支高素质专业化教师队伍，推动“两会”精神在学院十四五规划工作和高质量发展工作中落到实处。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"346\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/a9/73/349d947147cb9a0ec3f3e103bd88/be918645-15e5-4795-8d2c-4e4811792766.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" data-layer=\"photo\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/a9/73/349d947147cb9a0ec3f3e103bd88/be918645-15e5-4795-8d2c-4e4811792766_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'1.jpg\'}\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 346px;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-03-25 00:00:00', '2021-03-25 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:46:49', '', '2021-04-27 09:43:53', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (184, '信息工程学院召开党史学习教育动员部署会', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 等线;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">24</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日下午，信息工程学院在学院会议室召开党史学习教育动员部署会。学院领导班子成员，全体教职工参加会议。会议由院党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议学习了《习近平在党史学习教育动员大会上强调学党史悟思想办实事开新局以优异成绩迎接建党一百周年》，传达了校党委关于党史学习教育部署会的会议精神，重点学习了戴斌荣书记和方忠校长在校党史学习教育动员部署会上的讲话内容，要求强化主体责任、加强组织领导，学习了学校《关于党史学习教育的实施方案》等相关内容。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议强调，在庆祝中国共产党百年华诞的重大时刻、在“两个一百年”奋斗目标历史交汇的关键节点开展党史学习教育，对于总结历史经验、认识历史规律、传承红色基因、牢记初心使命、坚持正确方向、深入学习领会习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想，夺取新时代中国特色社会主义伟大胜利，具有重大而深远的意义。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 等线; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议要求，全体教职工务必在学校党委的统一领导下，统一思想，提高政治站位，以高度的政治自觉投入到党史学习教育中，不断坚定理想信念、筑牢初心使命</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">要把党史学习教育同自身工作相结合，同教师队伍教育整顿相结合，统筹兼顾、知行合一</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">“学党史、悟思想、办实事、开新局”，努力推动学院学校事业高质量发展，以优异成绩迎接建党一百周年。</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"346\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/0f/1e/25f7339a420baf4062fe02c0c722/41bf0eb3-5322-4130-abae-10a15ab1762f.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'$%2%83(57AGUL]`}NW13XDR.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/0f/1e/25f7339a420baf4062fe02c0c722/41bf0eb3-5322-4130-abae-10a15ab1762f_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 346px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '2021-03-25 00:00:00', '2021-03-25 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:47:12', '', '2021-04-27 09:43:44', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (185, '信息工程学院工会为教师过集体生日', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">为了让教师们在忙碌的工作之余留下一份甜蜜的回忆，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">24</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日，信息工程学院工会为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">1-3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月份出生的教师在党员之家举行集体生日会。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">下午三点，集体过生日的教师们齐聚党员之家。生日会上，院工会主席姜琳为教师们送上真挚而又温馨的祝福，院党委书记赵任凭、院长朱立才给老师们送出精心准备的生日大礼包，并和教师们共同点燃生日蛋糕，唱响生日快乐歌。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">在悠扬的音乐声中，大家相互送上了祝福与鼓励，分享香甜可口的生日蛋糕。一句句暖暖的问候，一份份学院的关怀，让“寿星”老师们脸上堆满了温暖幸福的笑容。整个活动在欢声笑语中达到了高潮，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">掌声、笑声、声声入耳；亲情、友情、情情暖心。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">集体生日会虽简单但十分温馨，体现出学院对教师们的关爱，拉近了教师之间的距离，增强了团队凝聚力，相信生日会上的温馨时刻，不仅能留在每一位教师的心中，也会芬芳他们今后的教育路程，鼓励学院教师不忘初心，牢记使命，为党的教育事业奋斗终身。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"1027\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/9a/24/32eb3d0d485191f953fa96a53d34/4d25f47e-75e3-46db-b2bf-7c8ac2318b4f.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'1.jpg\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 1027px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-03-25 00:00:00', '2021-03-25 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:47:33', '', '2021-04-27 09:35:59', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (186, '信息工程学院2021年春学期入党积极分子暨青马工程培训班顺利开班', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">30</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，信息工程学院在通榆校区主楼国会中心举行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">2021</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">年春学期入党积极分子暨青马工程培训班开班仪式。学院党委书记赵任凭出席开班仪式并讲话。会议由学院学生支部书记卞雅妮主持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">开班仪式在庄严的国歌声中拉开序幕。卞雅妮简要介绍了学院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">2021</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">年入党积极分子暨青马工程培训计划和相关纪律要求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">入党积极分子软件工程</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">195</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">班付梦雨同学作了表态发言，表示将认真参与课程培训，以实际行动努力向党组织靠拢，积极发挥先进模范带头作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会上，赵任凭向入党积极分子和青马工程培训学员提出了三点希望：一是要提升自身理想信念，坚定政治方向。思想是行动的先导，信仰是行动的航标。全体学员要把加入党组织作为政治立场和政治信仰的坚定选择，要用党的十九大精神和习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想武装头脑、指导实践；二是要加强政治理论学习，提高政治水平。大学生要以学为本，全体学员在学好专业知识的同时，更要系统地学习习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想，学习党的基本知识，加强对党的全面了解，学习马克思主义基本理论，结合“四史”学习，投身党史学习教育活动中，运用好“学习强国”等平台，努力学习政治理论，不断提升政治水平；三是加强实践学习，锤炼政治品格。作为新时代的大学生，要学理论读“有字之书”，更要强实践读“无字之书”，要在实践中磨砺品格，关注社会现实，关心国家发展，自觉投身中国第二个百年宏伟目标的建设中，为中华民族伟大复兴作出青年大学生应有的贡献。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">最后，赵任凭以《中国共产党的成立》为题，开启了入党积极分子的党课学习。课堂内容从五四运动和马克思主义的传播、党的早期组织的建立、党的一大召开和中国共产党创立意义等四个方面展开。详细讲解了中国共产党成立前后的党史内容，突出讲解了中国共产党的成立是开天辟地的大事变，中国共产党的成立深刻改变了近代以后中华民族发展的方向和进程，改变了中国人民和中华民族的前途和命运，改变了世界发展的趋势和格局。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">入党积极分子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">207</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">班左昕玉表示：“身为一名入党积极分子，我一定会增强理想信念，提高思想觉悟，砥砺意志品质，练就过硬本领，争取早日成为一名光荣的正式党员。”</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"500\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/1d/7a/fb1a3d6e499e8e29e76eecb8f4a0/29b9d32c-350f-42a4-8b13-250729fc77af.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" data-layer=\"photo\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/1d/7a/fb1a3d6e499e8e29e76eecb8f4a0/29b9d32c-350f-42a4-8b13-250729fc77af_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'1.jpg\'}\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"500\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/1d/7a/fb1a3d6e499e8e29e76eecb8f4a0/1d3583e0-6d69-4e39-95d6-e286e9860069.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" data-layer=\"photo\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/1d/7a/fb1a3d6e499e8e29e76eecb8f4a0/1d3583e0-6d69-4e39-95d6-e286e9860069_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'2.jpg\'}\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"500\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/1d/7a/fb1a3d6e499e8e29e76eecb8f4a0/b008879f-5f60-41b4-9b37-f2bd1ff53863.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" data-layer=\"photo\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/1d/7a/fb1a3d6e499e8e29e76eecb8f4a0/b008879f-5f60-41b4-9b37-f2bd1ff53863_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'3.jpg\'}\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-04-05 00:00:00', '2021-04-05 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:48:03', '', '2021-04-27 09:35:51', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (187, '信息工程学院召开意识形态工作专题学习会', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">4</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">7</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日下午，信息工程学院召开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">2021</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">年春学期全体教职工第四次思想政治（意识形态专题）学习研讨会。学院班子成员及全体教职工参加会议，会议由党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会上，赵任凭领学了《新时代党的意识形态工作的指导纲领》，阐述了抓好意识形态工作的迫切性和重要性，提出要坚持马克思主义在意识形态领域指导地位的根本制度，牢牢掌握意识形态工作的领导权、管理权、话语权；坚定正确的理想信念，做好宣传工作；高度重视网上舆论工作，打造风清气正的网络环境；坚定文化自信，牢牢把握社会主义先进文化的前进方向；加强话语体系建设，构建中国特色哲学社会体系；抓好高校意识形态工作，培养堪当民族大任的新时代奋斗者；增强阵地意识，认真落实意识形态工作责任制等九方面对习近平总书记关于意识形态工作的重要论述展开学习。会上，着重对抓好高校意识形态工作，培养堪当民族大任的新时代奋斗者这一内容进行了精准解读。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会上，院党委委员、办公室主任徐贵伍和学工办主任季芳芳就学习内容，联系自己的工作实际，分别从教师和学生意识形态工作的现状、面临的问题、解决的措施等三方面进行了交流学习。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议指出，党的十八大以来，习近平总书记就意识形态工作作出一系列重要论述，进一步深化了我们党对意识形态工作规律性的认识，为我们做好意识形态工作提供了根本遵循。高校是社会思潮的集散地，首当其冲的是青年学生，他们迫切需要旗帜鲜明而又循循善诱的引导。我院全体教职工务必要把立德树人作为根本任务，肩负起培养德智体美劳全面发展的社会主义建设者和接班人的重大任务。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议强调，能否做好意识形态工作，事关党的前途命运，事关国家长治久安，事关民族凝聚力和向心力。要充分认识意识形态工作的极端重要性，切实增强责任感和使命感，</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">要把意识形态工作作为学院十四五规划工作和高质量发展工作的重要内容，融入管党治党全过程和各方面。</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">要</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">在基础性、战略性工作上下功夫，在关键处、要害处下功夫，树立底线思维，突出问题导向，深入扎实做好意识形态各项工作，真正把党管意识形态要求全面具体落到实处。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"346\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/27/25/805997344c46a93fd347370d7815/05e35767-4760-4a30-aff8-8c7b6a179d7f.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'IP`XH_XWWJ4{AFP9N63EFD7.JPG\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/27/25/805997344c46a93fd347370d7815/05e35767-4760-4a30-aff8-8c7b6a179d7f_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 346px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"346\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/27/25/805997344c46a93fd347370d7815/616ec14e-a9ca-46c0-9883-6ba9f71c07a4.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'Q`53P4]3TTA)QEHACU$)XGD.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/27/25/805997344c46a93fd347370d7815/616ec14e-a9ca-46c0-9883-6ba9f71c07a4_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 346px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-04-08 00:00:00', '2021-04-08 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:48:23', '', '2021-04-27 09:34:22', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (188, '信息工程学院召开基层团组织书记述职评议大会', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日晚，信息工程学院在会议室召开基层团组织书记述职评议大会。会议由院团总支书记卞雅妮主持，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">18</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">19</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">20</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">级团支书参会。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会上，各班团支书围绕“思想引领”、“组织建设”、“支部特色”和“社会实践”等方面依次进行述职汇报，通过分析存在的问题，找出整改措施。把职责摆进去；把问题根源讲透彻；把整改方向找明确。卞雅妮和团总支工作人员秉持着公平公正的原则，认真按照评议细则，准备相关材料，实事求是给予评分。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">述职结束后，卞雅妮对各团支书的述职内容进行点评，充分肯定大家的工作成绩，并指出存在的问题。她强调，各团支书要保持热情、积极进取，在思想上引领团员青年向组织靠拢，要依托专业开展特色团日活动，做好社会实践活动，以朋辈的力量去影响班集体，充分发挥团的战斗堡垒作用。最后，卞雅妮就我院团总支近一年来的工作进行总结汇报。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">本次述职评议大会的顺利召开，体现了学院对青年团员思想教育的重视，加强团支部的战斗力和凝聚力，有效增强团组织内部的建设。会后各支部书记们纷纷表示将继续为团组织建设再上新台阶贡献青春力量。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"269\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/de/51/651cc0d440549416e9b599641dab/fa9c3bab-459e-4514-b436-199aac863bf2.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'0L39MJRRR%N%]{3){QX@JTC.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 269px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"270\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/de/51/651cc0d440549416e9b599641dab/1c1c5ae2-00c6-4295-b4b4-b16ebdc3b2d5.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\']KP1OCFKE9TDY(@S)Y}F(E8.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 270px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-04-08 00:00:00', '2021-04-08 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:48:43', '', '2021-04-27 09:32:48', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (189, '信息工程学院深入开展“云追思·致敬英烈”党史学习教育系列活动', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">为深入推进党史学习教育，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">-5</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日，信息工程学院组织开展形式多样的清明节“云追思·致敬英烈”主题活动，传承红色基因，弘扬中国传统文化，厚植爱党爱国情怀。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">红色微视频制作，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">学习党史守初心。</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">清明雨上，烈士浩气，万古长青；折菊雨下，后辈优思，抚今追昔。清明节“学党史——云追思，致敬英烈”红色微视频制作活动得到同学们的积极响应，诵读红色家书、讲述红色故事、交流经典红色影片观后感、重温英雄感人事迹，同学们用自己真挚的语言传递红色星火，展现报国之志。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/25/0b/7eabc1c646d1a0685bf720cbed82/b7182626-63f2-44bc-af6a-d7adf5307799.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'ZDY$F4Q7XIG`L){ZW08)C`R.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 267px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"263\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/25/0b/7eabc1c646d1a0685bf720cbed82/f4988dd3-d76c-47fc-a2ab-f98ff461a551.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'DQ@SMX8SA`)1~X25W}V5GPI.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 263px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">青春“云祭扫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">活动</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，致敬英烈担使命。</span></span></span><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">铭记，是为了更好前行，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">同学们积极参加清明节</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">云祭扫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">活动。网上献花、点烛、上香、鞠躬、默哀、留言</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">“祭英烈之灵，筑中华之魂”、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">铭记历史，缅怀先烈，追忆先辈”，同学们用文明祭扫的实际行动，向英勇献身的烈士们表达深深的敬意和哀思，并纷纷表示：</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">一代人有一代人的历史使命，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">要发扬先烈们的革命精神，秉承革命遗志，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">走好我们这一代青年人的长征路</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">。</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"267\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/25/0b/7eabc1c646d1a0685bf720cbed82/df7add63-930c-45b2-aa69-c69346a86613.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'(2X39IO~K3F@9$IX7XK)D4U.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/25/0b/7eabc1c646d1a0685bf720cbed82/df7add63-930c-45b2-aa69-c69346a86613_d.png\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 267px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"268\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/25/0b/7eabc1c646d1a0685bf720cbed82/a88b4278-4034-4a67-b675-bb8d5f572b41.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'2MZOT9DCSKUO(ZNG]`SP05F.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 268px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">清明主题诗词竞赛</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">，传承文化强信念</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">。</span></span></span><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">清明节主题诗词竞赛活动，在追思英烈中弘扬传统文化，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">汲取奋进的智慧和力量</span><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">。同学们纷纷表示：“品读古代诗歌里的清明，是一种情感的寄托，更是一份文化的传承。”、“生者寻根，叶落归根；有人烟处，必有血脉传承。”、“</span><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">传承红色基因，革命薪火的同时</span><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">增加了我们的文化自信。”</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"260\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/25/0b/7eabc1c646d1a0685bf720cbed82/66070b0e-5190-436d-baea-72ba1c337f87.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'`[B3T3TB~IVOJIAKSE[L5NV.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/25/0b/7eabc1c646d1a0685bf720cbed82/66070b0e-5190-436d-baea-72ba1c337f87_d.png\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 260px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"481\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/25/0b/7eabc1c646d1a0685bf720cbed82/c420a013-86cc-4434-a78c-7ede269f3158.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'C1O5NZQB7FWWXJ)EJD]RLUS.png\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 481px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">天地英雄气，千秋尚凛然。此次“云追思·致敬英烈”党史学习教育系列活动的开展，展现了信息工程学院学子积极响应学校、学院号召，学史明理、学史增信、学史崇德、学史力行，争做勇挑重担、攻坚克难，堪当大任的新时代中国青年的决心！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-04-09 00:00:00', '2021-04-09 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:49:09', '', '2021-04-27 09:32:39', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (190, '信息工程学院组织校外实训学生开展学党史·参观当地红色教育基地活动', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 1cm; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">学百年党史、传承红色基因，为扎实有序开展好党史学习教育，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">4</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">9</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日下午，信息工程学院组织国家一流专业建设点“软件工程”专业——软件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">“187</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">铁军班</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">、软件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">186</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">班学生党员、发展对象和入党积极分子，参观如皋市红色教育基地——中国工农红军第十四纪念馆，缅怀革命先辈，传承红军精神，激发爱国主义情怀。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 34px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">同学们有序参观了中国工农红军第十四纪念馆，认真聆听讲解、瞻仰珍贵的历史照片和展品、深切缅怀老一辈革命先烈。在纪念馆内，全体党员面向党旗庄严宣誓，重温入党誓词，要对党忠诚担当，牢记初心使命。最后交流环节，同学们纷纷表示，精神上得到了洗礼，要倍加珍惜今天和平、安定的幸福生活，为实现民族复兴中国梦而努力学习。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 34px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">软件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">187</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">班班长、预备党员杨雨琦同学说：“通过此次参观学习，我受到了一次深刻的党性教育，增强了爱党爱国、爱社会主义的自豪感。在今后的学习中，我将带领“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">187</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">铁军班”，乘着学院“软件工程”国家一流专业建设的东风，以更加昂扬的斗志，积极开展党史学习教育，在党史中汲取奋进的智慧和力量，为信息工程学院发展添砖加瓦。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 34px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">目前，软件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">“187</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">铁军班</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">”</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">、软件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">186</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">班正在如皋中软国际教育基地进行为期一学期校外企业实训。信息工程学院高度重视校外实训学生的党建与政治思想教育工作，正在积极筹建校企合作功能型党支部，促进学校和企业党建优势资源互补，实现党员在哪里，党建工作就覆盖到哪里。</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"521\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/80/73/741bae1f43faad879128620ca6b4/ef03c910-dbb5-40f4-8dfc-ba02349cfcd7.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'1.jpg\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 521px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"625\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/80/73/741bae1f43faad879128620ca6b4/cc018c28-7aef-4272-8a70-ed3112b56d5c.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'2.jpg\'}\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 625px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-04-11 00:00:00', '2021-04-11 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:49:31', '', '2021-04-27 09:32:20', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (191, '信息工程学院教工第一党支部召开4月份主题党日活动', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">4月21日上午，信息工程学院教工第一党支部在学院党员之家召开“学党史、悟思想、办实事、开新局”4月份主题党日活动。第一党支部全体党员同志参加，支部书记季芳芳主持活动。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">会上，同志们共同学习了四本必读书目</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">——习近平同志《论中国共产党历史》、《毛泽东邓小平江泽民胡锦涛关于中国共产党历史论述摘编》、《习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想学习问答》、《中国共产党简史》的主要内容和重要意义，明确了必须把四本必读书目融会贯通起来学习，才能系统全面地弄清楚历史事件的来龙去脉，把握党的历史发展的主题主线、主流本质，真正做到学党史、悟思想、办实事、开新局；领学了《毛泽东邓小平江泽民胡锦涛关于中国共产党历史论述摘编》“邓小平重要论述”《改革开放使中国真正活跃起来》、《总结历史是为了开辟未来》等重要内容；观看了教育纪录片《铁军》（第二集：鏖战敌后）及党建电视专栏《领航新时代》，并结合本职工作开展学习交流，深刻领会学习材料的丰富内涵和精神实质。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\">随后，第一党支部集中观看习近平在清华大学考察的新闻联播、学习重要讲话精神、交流学习心得。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/b7/3b/08a6c8c14e8ab15832bbe2c927d9/dba7a4b1-e8fc-4f33-8dd7-5e8eeef4329b.png\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'图片1.png\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"743\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"float: none; width: 750px; height: 743px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/b7/3b/08a6c8c14e8ab15832bbe2c927d9/470b6c62-dcae-4ef0-b582-a28abb84291a.png\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'图片2.png\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"564\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"float: none; width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-04-22 00:00:00', '2021-04-22 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:49:52', '', '2021-04-27 09:31:54', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (192, '信息工程学院师生热议习近平总书记19日在清华大学考察时的重要讲话精神', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 30px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">4月21日，信息工程学院组织广大师生认真收看习近平总书记19日在清华大学考察时发表的重要讲话视频，并展开热烈的交流与讨论。大家表示，要牢记总书记</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">殷切教诲，</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">全面贯彻党的教育方针、培育时代新人、立志做一流人才，为服务国家富强、民族复兴、人民幸福贡献应有的力量。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.5px; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">学院党委副书记、副院长姜琳说，今年是中国共产党成立</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">100周年，习近平总书记在清华大学考察时发表的重要讲话，充分体现了党中央对高等教育的高度重视，对高校师生的亲切关怀。信息工程学院紧紧围绕立德树人根本任务，牢记使命，为党育人、为国育才。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">教工第一支部书记季芳芳说</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">总书记</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">的重要</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">讲话令人倍感振奋</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">！</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">作为一名高校教师</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">，我要始终同党和人民站在一起，自觉做中国特色社会主义的坚定信仰者和忠实者。我要认真做好本职工作，加强自我学习，提升能力和水平，</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">争做新时代</span><span style=\"line-height: 30px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">“四有好老师”， 全心全意服务学生的成长成才。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.5px; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">副科级辅导员毛阿璇说，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">“教师要成为大先生，做学生为学、为事、为人的示范，促使学生成为全面发展的人。”习近平总书记的重要讲话为我们指明前进的方向。作为一线思政工作者，我深感肩上责任重大，努力为党和人民的教育事业奋斗终身。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.5px; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">国家一流专业建设点软件工程</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">196班团支书闵小晶同学说：“观看习近平总书记考察清华大学的重要讲话后，我感触颇深。身为信工学子，我们在课堂上学到了先进的计算机技术，深刻意识到科技对生活带来的巨大影响。我要努力学习专业知识，努力成为能堪当民族复兴重任的时代新人。”</span></span></p><p class=\"15\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">数媒</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">197班王永林同学说：“</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">作为新时代</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">青年，青春的底色是爱国，爱国是流淌在骨子里的责任。我们要坚持正确的政治方向，不负总书记的嘱托，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">坚定</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">理想信念，不断提升自我，稳扎稳打学好专业知识，勇攀知识高峰，为实现中华民族伟大复兴贡献自己的青春力量。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">”</span></span></p><p class=\"15\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">计算机</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\">192班王正中同学说：“总书记指出广大青年要爱国爱民、锤炼品德、勇于创新、实学实干。我们生逢盛世肩负重任，要牢记总书记的教诲，要立大志、明大德，抓紧时间，刻苦学习，成大才、担大任，让青春在为祖国、为民族、为人民、为人类的不懈奋斗中绽放绚丽之花。”</span></span></p><p class=\"15\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/d5/ac/ef56da184d29b7393d06254e7578/577c90cf-43aa-4b14-916c-96ec4de4c4a5.png\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'图片1.png\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"564\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"float: none; width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/d5/ac/ef56da184d29b7393d06254e7578/27646785-7d16-4295-b3a4-70676da086a4.png\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/d5/ac/ef56da184d29b7393d06254e7578/27646785-7d16-4295-b3a4-70676da086a4_d.png\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'图片2.png\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"564\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"float: none; width: 750px; height: 564px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img data-layer=\"photo\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/d5/ac/ef56da184d29b7393d06254e7578/cefe8a54-e386-4672-b136-f3310be18183.jpg\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/d5/ac/ef56da184d29b7393d06254e7578/cefe8a54-e386-4672-b136-f3310be18183_d.jpg\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\'1111.jpg\'}\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"float: none; width: 750px; height: 750px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-04-22 00:00:00', '2021-04-22 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:50:19', '', '2021-04-27 09:31:46', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (193, '信息工程学院组织集中观看《习近平在清华大学110周年校庆日的考察视频》', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">为深入贯彻落实习近平总书记在清华大学</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">110</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">周年校庆日考察时的重要讲话精神，深刻领会习总书记为高等教育发展勾画的蓝图，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">4</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">21</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">日下午，信息工程学院在会议室组织全体教职工集中观看</span></span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">《习近平在清华大学</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">110</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">周年校庆日的考察视频》</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">。活动由党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">习近平总书记先后视察了清华大学美术学院、成像与智能技术实验室、重点教学科研成果展示、西体育馆，了解了学校深化改革、人才队伍建设、教学科研创新和服务国家发展等情况。随后，习近平与师生代表座谈并发表重要讲话。习近平强调百年大计，教育为本。在中国共产党成立</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">100</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">周年之际，我国开启了全面建设社会主义现代化新征程，党和国家事业发展对高等教育的需要，</span></span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">对科学知识和优秀人才的需要，比以往任何时候都更为迫切。我国社会主义教育就是要培养德智体美劳全面发展的社会主义建设者和接班人。我国高等教育要立足中华民族伟大复兴战略</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">全局和世界百年未有之大变局，努力建设中国特色的社会主义世界一流大学。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 37px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">通过对《习近平在清华大学</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">110</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun;\">周年校庆日的考察视频》的学习，全体教职工热血澎湃，深刻领会了习近平总书记对我国高等教育事业发展的重视，了解了党和国家对高等教育事业发展的迫切需求，纷纷表示要坚持把立德树人作为根本任务，不断提高人才培养质量，着力培养担当民族复兴大任的时代新人。</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 30.8px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"346\" src=\"http://ist.yctu.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/ba/da/d86db8c14dcb9bd6bf181fcac2a4/8c566c15-d8b7-4594-b94d-9c42778a4ebb.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" sudyfile-attr=\"{\'title\':\']1X}R_98~1DENH@DTY1(X64.jpg\'}\" original-src=\"/_upload/article/images/ba/da/d86db8c14dcb9bd6bf181fcac2a4/8c566c15-d8b7-4594-b94d-9c42778a4ebb_d.jpg\" data-layer=\"photo\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 346px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-04-22 00:00:00', '2021-04-22 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:50:55', '', '2021-04-27 09:31:29', '');
INSERT INTO `sys_news_documentary` VALUES (194, '信息工程学院召开2021年度第四次党委理论学习中心组（扩大）学习会', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 16px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">4</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">21</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">日上午，信息工程学院党委在党员之家召开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">2021</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">年第四次党委理论学习中心组（扩大）学习会，学院党委成员、各支部书记以及科级干部参加学习。会议由党委书记赵任凭主持。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">党委书记赵任凭领学了《教育部等八部门关于加快构建高校思想政治工作体系的意见》、《人民政协在建立新中国和社会主义革命、建设、改革各个历史时期发挥了十分重要的作用》。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议强调，要把思想政治工作贯穿教育教学全过程，运用社会和学校中一切可能的力量做好大学生思想政治工作，加强高校思政工作，要把遵循思想政治规律、教书育人规律、学生成长规律统筹起来，把领导格局、工作格局、反馈格局统筹起来，共同推动形成高校“大思政”体系，加快培养担当民族复兴大任的时代新人，培养德智体美劳全面发展的社会主义建设者和接班人。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会议指出，七十多年的实践证明，人民政协制度具有多方面的独特优势。中国式民主在中国行得通、很管用。新形势下，我们必须把人民政协制度坚持好、把人民政协事业发展好，增强开展统一战线工作的责任担当，把更多的人团结在党的周围。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">会上还为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">4</span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, simsun; font-size: 20px;\">月份入党的荀启峰老师过了“政治生日”，朱立才院长为荀启峰发放了政治生日纪念卡，荀启峰深情回顾了入党以来的成长历程，表示第一次收到属于自己的政治生日贺卡，更增强了自己党员的身份意识，表示一定积极进取，争当模范，为学院学校事业发展贡献自己力量。与会人员对荀启峰踏实细致、任劳任怨的工作作风给予了一致的肯定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><br></p>', '', '2021-04-24 00:00:00', '2021-04-24 00:00:00', '1', '', '1', 'admin', '2021-04-24 18:51:21', '', '2021-04-27 09:30:26', '');
